# Runtime-generated files — should not be committed.
# Inputs/Weekly Schedules/ is populated by uploads (local copy of Storage)
# Outputs/<week>/ is populated by each fill_engine run
# Archive/Grave Placement Archive.xlsx is mutated in place by the engine
#
# These files exist so the engine can run; they're not source code.

Inputs/Weekly Schedules/*.xlsx
Inputs/Weekly Schedules/_archive/
Outputs/*/
__pycache__/
*.pyc

# Keep the directory shells (and the active starting Archive xlsx) tracked
!Inputs/Weekly Schedules/.gitkeep
!Outputs/.gitkeep
